#: ../../B/BDFL.rst:5
msgid "BDFL"
msgstr "BDFL"

#: ../../B/BDFL.rst:7
msgid ""
"[Python; common] Benevolent Dictator For Life. :ref:`Guido`\\, considered in"
" his role as the project leader of :ref:`Python`\\. People who are feeling "
"temporarily cheesed off by one of his decisions sometimes leave off the B. "
"The mental image that goes with this, of a cigar-chomping caudillo in gold "
"braid and sunglasses, is extremely funny to anyone who has ever met Guido in"
" person."
msgstr ""
"[Python。一般的]Benevolent Dictator For Life(慈悲深い終身独裁者)。\\ :ref:`Python`\\ "
"のプロジェクトリーダーという役割における\\ :ref:`Guido`\\ "
"を指す。彼の決定の一つに一時的にむっとしている人は、Bを省くことがある。これに伴う心象——金モールとサングラスを身につけ葉巻をくわえた\\ "
"*カウディーリョ*\\ (独裁者)——は、Guidoに実際に会ったことのある者には実におかしい。"
